#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:4
msgid "Caravan"
msgstr "Caravana"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Caravan.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Caravans are used to carry gold or supplies long distances. Because of the "
"immense weight of the cargo this caravan carries, it moves very slowly."
msgstr ""
"Las caravanas se emplean para transportar oro o provisiones a través de "
"grandes distancias. Debido el inmenso peso de su cargamento, se mueven muy "
"lentamente."

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Arcanister"
msgstr "Maestro arcano enano"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The most powerful of all the runecrafters, the Dwarvish Arcanister destroys "
"wounded enemies almost instantly, and rarely fails to cause a wound when "
"that is his intent. His skill in runecrafting is unrivaled, and the glyphs "
"he carves into his weapons and armor deflect the blows of his enemies."
msgstr ""
"El más poderoso de todos los expertos rúnicos, el maestro arcano enano, "
"destruye enemigos heridos casi al instante, y raramente falla en darle a su "
"blanco cuando lo desea. Sus habilidades en la herrería rúnica no tienen "
"rival, y los glifos que graba en sus armas y armadura desvían los ataques de "
"sus enemigos."

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:26
#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Arcanister.cfg:27
#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runesmith.cfg:29
msgid "hammer"
msgstr "martillo"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Miner"
msgstr "Minero enano"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Dwarvish miners are the grunt workers of Dwarvish society. They take the "
"precious ores out of the ground, but do not ever take part in the crafting "
"of weapons or artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Los mineros enanos son la fuerza de trabajo de la sociedad Enana. Extraen "
"los preciosos materiales de la tierra, pero jamás toman parte en la "
"fabricación de armas o artefactos."

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Miner.cfg:19
msgid "pick"
msgstr "pica"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Runemaster"
msgstr "Maestro rúnico enano"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runemaster.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Except for those with almost supernatural skill, the highest rank a "
"runecrafter can rise to is that of the Dwarvish Runemaster. Striking blows "
"nearly as powerful as those of the best warriors, they would be fearsome "
"without their craft, but with it they are also nigh on invincible, since "
"their runes cause the physical blows of their enemies to deal less damage "
"than would be expected."
msgstr ""
"Salvo por aquellos con habilidades casi sobrenaturales, el mayor rango al "
"que puede llegar un herrero rúnico es el de maestro rúnico. Asestando golpes "
"casi tan poderosos como los de los mejores guerreros, serían temibles sin "
"sus artesanías, pero con éstas son casi invencibles, puesto que sus runas "
"hacen que los ataques físicos de sus enemigos causen menos daño de lo "
"esperado."

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runesmith.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Runesmith"
msgstr "Herrero rúnico enano"

#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/units/Dwarvish_Runesmith.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Dwarvish runesmiths, now practiced at their craft, carve arcane runes into "
"their weapons and armor. These runes infuse the runesmith's blows with power "
"and accuracy, and disrupt the blows of their enemies, causing them to strike "
"softly, weakly and on the armor of the defender."
msgstr ""
"Los herreros rúnicos enanos, experimentados en sus artesanías, cincelan "
"runas arcanas en sus armas y armadura. Éstas otorgan poder y precisión a los "
"golpes del herrero, y debilitan los golpes de sus enemigos, haciendo que "
"golpeen suave y débilmente contra la armadura del herrero."

